    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "plenty of docs: \n\nhttp://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/10min.html\nhttp://pandas.pydata.org/pandas-docs/stable/tutorials.html\n\n```\nIn [4]: df = DataFrame(np.random.randn(5,3),columns=list('abc'))\n\nIn [5]: df\nOut[5]: \n          a         b         c\n0  0.682791  0.195050  0.251640\n1  0.735865  1.435929 -0.556519\n2  0.466348 -1.497200  2.913788\n3 -1.439502  0.341941  0.571804\n4 -1.325086  0.516505  0.267241\n\nIn [6]: df['a']\nOut[6]: \n0    0.682791\n1    0.735865\n2    0.466348\n3   -1.439502\n4   -1.325086\nName: a, dtype: float64\n\nIn [7]: df[['a']]\nOut[7]: \n          a\n0  0.682791\n1  0.735865\n2  0.466348\n3 -1.439502\n4 -1.325086\n\nIn [8]: df[['a','b']]\nOut[8]: \n          a         b\n0  0.682791  0.195050\n1  0.735865  1.435929\n2  0.466348 -1.497200\n3 -1.439502  0.341941\n4 -1.325086  0.516505\n```\n"
